Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:47.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:48.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:49.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:55.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:59.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:12.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:16.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:26.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:39.33,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:29.80,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:38.39,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:47.11,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:47.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:48.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:49.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:55.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:59.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.41,0:23:03.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:05.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:12.88,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:16.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:21.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:26.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:39.33,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对自己的脆弱感到震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对泷老师的妻子说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拿下金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想替泷老师实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吹得越来越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:09.07,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}最后的竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你父亲联系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于  明天就要正式比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不要紧张  保持冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想平时那样去演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小笠原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么调音降B调
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\pos(760,985)}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿辉  你这牌太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负上不能手软
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用尽一切手段获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在都一直是平民…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  差不多要熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正正黑_GBK\fs84\bord0\1c&H213642&\pos(1312,432)}礼品柜台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的动作好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  原来是秀一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你穿成这样不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉有点不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是害怕竞赛会结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  忘记给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直没有机会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  你一直带在身上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在打开看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这礼物非常可爱  这是你选的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该喜欢这种花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我有说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是川岛她很兴奋地告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻美子姐的事  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你很沮丧的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你们以前姐妹关系那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是坂江高中  关东强校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小泷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的之前也有看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西城女子高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这3年来全都打进了全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清良女子高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了各位  丝带都戴好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我放哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戴好了  戴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打击乐器的通道和别的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来终于要正式比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在春天定下了打进全国大赛的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路前进到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意结果这种话我不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  既然站上了这个舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先最重要的就是  吹奏一场不让自己后悔的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是最后的正式演奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这华丽的舞台上奉献一场无悔的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  能让我说几句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  请说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到正式比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我绝对不会说任何消极的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  现在从心底感到激动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们吹奏出好的演奏  取得金奖回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  有请副部长明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于全国大赛  我给大家添了不少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能像现在这样站在这里  都是多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就由在这的全体北宇治学生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为大家吹奏一场最棒的音乐盛宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  让我们以微笑结束这场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家听我致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么大家和我一起喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的是最棒的簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说葵来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了来看特意去弄了张票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这票的抽选很难中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实今天  我姐姐也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那黄前你也必须加油才行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3号参赛学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关西代表  北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙  刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要买那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  为什么都买2张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1张是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收藏用吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太低估你这强校控了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  接下来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离结果发布还有一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有咖啡店  我想去坐会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  不去听演奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可是部长和副部长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长和副部长的任职已经结束了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就三个人一起去吃巧克力香蕉巴菲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点一个特制的大号巧克力香蕉巴菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的话  就让他们做一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来将进行高中部后半场的颁奖典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么首先
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向参加本次竞赛会的各位指挥颁发指挥奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥奖？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}时间关系以下敬称省略\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}山岡博之\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是颁发给每个学校指挥的奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果发表在这个之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}小山  最喜欢你了\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  把这个给忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  我们什么都没准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃木彻平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻平老师超级大帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候那2个人却在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷升
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来说点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉崎修介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉崎老师谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这种地方告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没把这当成是告白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在公布高中部后半场的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1号参赛学校  义雁商业高中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖状  银奖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中部门
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}义雁商业高中\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽奈她是不是喜欢老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把精神集中在颁奖上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2号参赛学校  片敷高中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3号参赛学校  北宇治高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这无精打采的表情是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我点笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是高坂同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的实力就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:15:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年一定要拿到金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你刚才的助威
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我有点没自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到那个我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是把自己想做的事强加给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以觉得大家并不喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很尊敬泷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样得话  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  我来北宇治就是因为有老师您在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的喜欢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能这么说  作为老师我很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常棒的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都听哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小笠原  你很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月  你这么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家那么努力  却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月  你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人是可以改变一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的结果  到了明年就能改写成别的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月你不想比任何人都跳得高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就从最低的位置开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会比任何人都练习得更多的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中同学  黄前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好  我有话要和你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道进藤正和先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是今天的评委
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道  他是悠风号演奏家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我在走廊遇见他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他托付我给吹悠风号的同学带个口信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我很高兴你能坚持到现在」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「非常动听的乐声」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们中谁的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有些交集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的演奏被他表扬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢  学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三年生今天就此引退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后很感谢你们一直以来跟随我这个不中用的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这一年发生过很多不愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多事情要操心让人很不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和大家一起演奏的那种快乐  让这些都不值一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  让我代替爱哭鬼部长来说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  关于今天的演奏我并没有什么要说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治的演奏已经让全国都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们付出了全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们三年生会就此引退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是二年生的天下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对此充满了不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也知道我这个不会拐弯抹角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的结果我非常地不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是三年生已经没有雪耻的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种经历我们有过就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以明年你们一定要拿到金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后副部长命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  这个回答我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算毕业了我也会每天来看着你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  你这样太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  我喜欢悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有姐姐在  我才会喜欢上悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有姐姐在  我才会喜欢上吹奏乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
